We used the below steps to extract data for the visualizations related to organizations.

Step 1: access pdf of aggregated World Values Survey results for China (http://www.worldvaluessurvey.org/WVSDocumentationWV7.jsp) and for the US http://www.worldvaluessurvey.org/WVSDocumentationWV7.jsp).

Step 2: transcribe relevant data into a csv file (organizations-input.csv).

Step 3: convert to json using python (convert-organizations-data).
